                     <interp inst="t18470614-1538-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 1 coat, value 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18470614-name-1142" type="victimName">
