                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable M</hi> 94) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction at this Court—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted</hi> 21<hi rend="italic">st of Sept.</hi>, 1846, <hi rend="italic">and confined six months</hi>)—the prisoner is the person.</p>
